LG Chem to Suspend Investment in Polysilicon Business

-- B y   S a n g i m   H a n
-- 
2011-12-02T09:05:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-02/lg-chem-to-suspend-investment-in-polysilicon-business.html
LG Chem Ltd. (051910)  plans to suspend
investment in the polysilicon business until the outlook for the
sector improves, according to a regulatory filing today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
